name: Pocket Tee | Black x Burnt Orange
description: This shirt was produced in Bali using natural stonewashed Rayon* It is a regular fit with a round, loose neck line. The stone washing process gives the item a sketchy, vintage look so any imperfections, including fading and small perforations, are intended. All purchases come wrapped in recycled paper along with a sticker. *Rayon isn't synthetic or natural. WHAT? it's some crazy fibre cocktail. Also known as art silk in the textile industry, this naturally sourced fabrique makes for a wonderful partner and loyal friend in your wardrobe. Handle me with care; to ensure your shirt lives longer than you and the colour remains true, it is essential that this item is washed in COLD water, preferably hand washed.
